critic.com/news/2020/02/05/own-announces-tyler-perry-drama-if-loving-you-is-wrong-premieres-its-fifth-and-final-season-tuesday-march-10-718414/20200205own01/|work=[[The Futon Critic]]|date=February 5, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[You Me Her]]''\n| [[Audience (TV network)|Audience]]\n|rowspan=5| 2016\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/05/you-me-her-end-season-5-audience-network-1202612214/|title='You Me Her' To End With Season 5 On Audience Network|work=Deadline Hollywood|first=Denise|last=Petski|date=May 10, 2019|accessdate=October 12, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Goliath (TV series)|Goliath]]''\n| [[Prime Video|Amazon Prime Video]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/11/goliath-ending-season-four-last-billy-bob-thornton-amazon-1202786679/|title='Goliath' Renewed For Fourth And Final Season By Amazon|work=Deadline Hollywood|first=Patrick|last=Hipes|date=November 14, 2019|accessdate=November 21, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Van Helsing (TV series)|Van Helsing]]''\n| Syfy\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/van-helsing-renewed-fifth-and-final-season-at-syfy-1203445159/|title='Van Helsing' Renewed for Fifth and Final Season at Syfy|last=Thorne|first=Will|date=December 17, 2019|work=Variety|accessdate=December 19, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Fuller House (TV series)|Fuller House]]''\n|rowspan=5| Netflix\n|<ref>{{cite web|url= https://tvline.com/2019/11/20/fuller-house-season-5-premiere-date-final-episodes-preview/|title=''Fuller House''{{'s}} Final Season Gets December Premiere Date on Netflix|first=Andy|last=Swift|work=TVLine|date=November 20, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Lucifer (TV series)|Lucifer]]''\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/06/lucifer-renewed-season-5-final-season-netflix-1202628454/|title='Lucifer' Renewed For Fifth & Final Season By Netflix|first1=Nellie|last1=Andreeva|date=June 6, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[13 Reasons Why]]\n|rowspan=4| 2017\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/08/13-reasons-why-season-3-premier