ason2020\"/>\n|-\n| ''[[Shameless (American TV series)|Shameless]]''\n| Showtime\n| 2011\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Showtime(R) Announces 11th and Final Season of \"Shameless\" to Premiere This Summer|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2020/01/13/showtime-announces-11th-and-final-season-of-shameless-to-premiere-this-summer-541210/20200113showtime10/|work=[[The Futon Critic]]|date=January 13, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Doc McStuffins]]''\n| [[Disney Junior]]\n| 2012\n|<ref>{{cite tweet|number=981585098318389248|title=Yesterday marked the end of an era- I recorded my last episode of our last season of #DocMcStuffins. What an amazing journey I've had for the past 8 years. \"If you're a toy, then you're in luck.\" I sure was!! I've been so very lucky and blessed to be a part of... 1/2|user=LaraJillMiller|first=Lara Jill|last=Miller|date=April 4, 2018|accessdate=March 6, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite tweet|number=981641453276286976|title=8 years to do 5 seasons. And stay tuned for many new eps to premiere in 2018/19!|user=LaraJillMiller|first=Lara Jill|last=Miller|date=April 4, 2018|accessdate=March 6, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Vikings (2013 TV series)|Vikings]]''\n| [[History (U.S. TV network)|History]]\n| 2013\n|<ref>{{cite web|title='Vikings' To End After Season 6, Followup Series In Works At History From Michael Hirst & MGM Television|url=https://deadline.com/2019/01/vikings-to-end-season-6-final-season-followup-series-spinoff-history-michael-hirst-mgm-tv-1202528772/|work=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|accessdate=January 4, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[The 100 (TV series)|The 100]]''\n| The CW\n|rowspan=2| 2014\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/08/the-100-upcoming-seventh-season-will-be-last-on-the-cw-1202660843/|title='The 100': Upcoming Season 7 Will Be The Last For Sci-Fi Drama On The CW \u2013 TCA|first1=Peter|last1=White|date=August 4, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[If Loving You Is Wrong]]''\n| [[Oprah Winfrey Network]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=OWN Announces Tyler Perry Drama \