ic/news/bob-cobert-dead-dies-dark-shadows-winds-of-war-1203512992/ | title = Bob Cobert, \u2018Dark Shadows\u2019 and \u2018Winds of War\u2019 Composer, Dies at 95 | first = Jon | last = Burlingame | date = February 24, 2020 | accessdate = February 24, 2020 | work = [[Variety (magazine)|Variety]] }}</ref>\n|-\n|February 20\n|[[Sy Sperling]]\n|78\n|American consumer products executive, founder and spokesman of [[Hair Club]]\n|<ref>[http://www.startribune.com/hair-club-for-men-founder-and-client-sy-sperling-dies/568042192/ Hair Club for Men founder \u2014 and client \u2014 Sy Sperling dies] ''Minneapolis Star-Tribune'', February 20, 2020</ref>\n|-\n|February 22\n|[[B. Smith]]\n|70\n|American model, publisher, author, lifestyle designer, chef, and television personality (host of ''B. Smith With Style'', and made two appearances on ''[[Mister Rogers' Neighborhood]]'')\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/obituaries/b-smith-model-turned-restaurateur-and-lifestyle-maven-dies-at-70/2020/02/23/568c2066-5654-11ea-9000-f3cffee23036_story.html|title=B. Smith, model turned restaurateur and lifestyle maven, dies at 70|last=Langer|first=Emily|date=February 23, 2020|website=The Washington Post|language=en|url-status=live|access-date=February 23, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|February 25\n|[[Lee Phillip Bell]]\n|91\n|American television producer (''[[The Bold and the Beautiful]]'', ''[[The Young and the Restless]]'')\n|<ref>[https://www.soapoperadigest.com/content/tv-pioneer-lee-phillip-bell-passes-away/ TV Pioneer Lee Phillip Bell Passes Away] ''Soap Opera Digest'', February 26, 2020</ref>\n|}\n\n=== March ===\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|- \"\n!width=90| Date ||width=125| Name || Age ||class=\"unsortable\" |Notability || class=\"unsortable\" | Source\n|-\n| March 2\n| [[James Lipton]]\n| 93\n| American actor, writer, and host of ''[[Inside the Actors Studio]]''. Other TV credits include ''[[The Simpsons]]'', ''[[Arrested Development]]'', and ''[[Glee (TV series)|Glee]]''\n